title: King Flight School - Private Pilot Master Collection
description:
This is a collection of all King School videos I could find online, re-encoded for lower size. I have attempted to preserve the format, menus, titles, along with questions and answers. Please post a comment if there are any errors in the collection. And say "Thank you" - this was hard work. :)

Please observe the seeding policy: If you do not intend to seed, please wait until torrent has at least 10 seeds before starting your download. If you intend to seed after you download it, then go ahead and download now. You should always seed to a ratio of at least 1.

Please support the King Schools by purchasing their products. They have done an amazing job putting together these courses.

Contents:


Private Pilot Course

Complete course. 8 DVD&#039;s with review questions. Encoded DivX VBR Q=12 (300~500kbps), audio MP3 128kbps.



Private Pilot Practical Test Course

Going through a check ride: oral exam and flight test. 2 DVD&#039;s. Encoded DivX VBR Q=12 (300~500kbps), audio AC3 192kbps passthrough.



Airport Signs, Markings & Procedures

Going into detail around airports. 1 CDROM. Re-encoded MPEG-1 with VBR Q=12 for compression. Maintained directory structure so that it may be burned to CD-ROM to install and use the Questions & Answers program.



The Complete Airspace Review

Going into detail about airspace. 1 DVD. Encoded DivX VBR Q=12 (300~500kbps), audio AC3 192kbps passthrough.



Enjoy,
-snowcat24
